      • getCryptoToken

        CryptoToken getCryptoToken​(int cryptoTokenId)
        This method can be used whenever the authorization is implied. E.g. the caller had access to an object that references this CryptoToken and that reference cannot change.
        Parameters:
        cryptoTokenId - ID
        Returns:
        a reference to the cached and potentially active CryptoToken object.
